    "en": {
      "title": "A cigarette counts",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ceylon Tobacco Company says that the price of a cigarette has increased from 3 rupees to 15 rupees.",
        "This price increase is effective from yesterday (01) and the price of a cigarette of Captain type is 3 rupees, the price of a cigarette of Bristol and Golleaf types is 05 rupees. The price of a cigarette of Dunhill Switch and Dunhill Double Switch types is 10 rupees, Dunhill The company says that the price of a Blue Gray cigarette has also increased by 15 rupees.",
        "The Ceylon Tobacco Company added that the price of cigarettes has increased due to the increase in VAT from 12 to 15%."
      ],
